Reinforce Involvement and participation of Barangay through massive information dissemination of the Municipality’s Solid Waste Management programs;
Support the establishment of fully functional MRF for each Barangay or Cluster of Barangays. In the meantime, for barangays without MRF, provide appropriate and durable trash bins with proper labels on assigned collection areas;
Continue strict monitoring of areas where: (a) indiscriminate dumping of waste in rampant, if any; and (b) burning of wastes was being practiced;
Continue to enforce all regulations to the extent of imposing penalties for Non-Compliance; and
Hasten the construction of sanitary landfill.

